---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>

<!-- Background aesthetic -->
<div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-b 
            from-white/70 to-purple-50 
            dark:from-black/40 dark:to-zinc-900"></div>

<main
  class="px-6 py-24 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-neutral-800 
         dark:text-neutral-100 leading-relaxed 
         animate-fade-in"
>

  <!-- SECTION HEADER STYLE -->
  <style is:global>
    @keyframes fade-in {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- ================
       POEM 1
       ================ -->
  <section class="mb-24">
    <div class="mb-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight bg-gradient-to-r 
                 from-purple-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent 
                 pb-1">
        Violent bloom
      </h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-16 mx-auto bg-purple-300/50 dark:bg-purple-600/40"></div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/40 dark:bg-white/5 
             backdrop-blur-xl shadow-lg shadow-purple-200/30 
             dark:shadow-black/40 border border-white/30 
             dark:border-white/10"
    >
      <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed">
Violets are red, and Roses are blue
Life can be violent, yet flowers get through
Unleash your petals, get injured by thorns
When pain is built up, just try shifting hue

-Coughy
      </pre>
    </div>
  </section>


</main>

</BaseLayout>
